***Note:
- I probably broke this when I started breaking up the algorithm into one that computes uses an Averaging Hash and a hash relying on the DCT.

Requirements:
- Python Imaging Library (http://www.pythonware.com/products/pil/)
- OpenCV (http://opencv.willowgarage.com/wiki/)

Ubuntu Modules:
- python-opencv
- opencv-docs
- imagemagick
- libc-dev

Usage:
python face_detect.py  <input> <output>
python hash.py <image1> <image2>